  <li><a href="http://www.lungusa2.org/slati/appendixd.php"><strong>Amount of Revenue Collected by States from Cigarette Taxes in FY2012</strong></a> -<br />
  (July 1, 2011 to June 30, 2012 for most states)</li>
  <li><a href="http://www.lungusa2.org/slati/states.php"><strong>See your State&rsquo;s Tobacco Taxes</strong></a></li>
  <li><a href="http://www.stateoftobaccocontrol.org" target="_blank"><strong>See how your state measures up</strong></a></li>
</ul>
<h3>Other Resources:</h3>
